{"title":"“孝”子有方（外一首）","authors":["易和元"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":6,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孝”子有方（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易和元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬老早已不吃香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孝”子而今成风尚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子是主来父是仆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百依百随象绵羊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特权在手随意用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孝”子有方日夜忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果儿子想工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有安排不用慌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果儿子想当兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上穿上绿军装；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果儿子想出国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整装就教去留洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开阔眼界长见识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洋山洋水好风光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果儿子要月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘下玩玩又何妨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怪科学不发达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空怀壮志手不长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作牛作马心情愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛不闭不收场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孝”了儿子再“孝”孙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早忘革命为哪桩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“家长”脸谱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身在家庭是家长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身在机关“长”一家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独断专行成习惯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两耳爱听顺风话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺者高升逆者降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这叫有赏又有罚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要民主爱集中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官大权大本事大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三等九级层次明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高在上把令下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不懂装懂抖威风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说鹿是马就是马！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}